channel.title: Bulby 508 Error.. Again
channel.description:
I tried to add Grand Exchange, but i get this error.
[code].\Bulby\content\ge\GrandExchange.java:24: cannot access Bulby.content.ge.Offer bad class file: .\Bulby\content\ge\Offer.java file does not contain class Bulby.content.ge.Offer Please remove or make sure it appears in the correct subdirectory of the classpa th. public static List<Offer> offerList = new ArrayList<Offer>(2000); ^ .\Bulby\world\geLoader.java:10: cannot find symbol symbol : class geList location: class Bubly.world.geLoader public geList[] geList = new geList[maxListedItems]; ^ .\Bulby\world\geLoader.java:10: cannot find symbol symbol : class geList location: class Bubly.world.geLoader public geList[] geList = new geList[maxListedItems]; ^ .\Bulby\world\geLoader.java:66: cannot find symbol symbol : class geList location: class Bubly.world.geLoader geList[ItemId] = new geList(ItemId, buy, sell); ^ Note: .\Bulby\players\objectLoader.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Note: .\Bulby\clanchat\Room.java uses unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 3 errors[/code] What am I doing wrong?
